*************************************************************************
	Name: std-movies --- (Standard Movies Replacer Plugin)
	Version: 1.0
	Author: LINK/2012 <dma_2012@hotmail.com)
	Default Priority: 50
*************************************************************************

Description:
	The standard movies replacer is the standard plugin to handle movies files (mpg) in modloader.
	It replaces¹ the files GTAtitles.mpg / Logo.mpg
	
	¹ It does not replace in the sense of replacing on your filesystem, it replaces it on-the-fly.

Usage:
	Just place your GTAtitles.mpg or Logo.mpg into a mod folder, that simple.


Weakness and Limitations:
	[*] Limited to 4GB of dff/txd/col/etc mods
	[*] Needs double the size of the mods beucase it will create a copy of the files in another .img
		so, for example, if you have 50MB of cars (dff/txd), you need more 50MB for the temporary img,
		that's a total of 100MB.

